Title: 'Wanderlust '
DateModified: '2019-02-27'
DatePublished: '2019-02-27'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/wanderlust-5
SetInCountry: Korea South
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Mallika Paul
AuthorCountry: India
Text: This story is about a girl who always used to stay in her home and dont go anywhere
  outside.One day her mother suggested her to go out and travel so that she can experience
  how beautiful this life is.So she starts her travelling adventure and she decides
  to go to South Korea.Will she be able to understand how the actual life feels like
  and how it is different from staying in a closed space
